Initializes Engine and starts Full-HD mode conversion. Prepares the colorMap, sets the variables and starts generating the first line of the output.

Parameters:
id - the ImageData
scheme - the ColorScheme to use
preset - the CharacterSet to use
contrast - value will be multiplied with the rgb of each pixel
brightness - value will be added to the rgb of each pixel
